FIVE days before his birthday in December, Lawrence Khanye from Block GG in Soshanguve, north of Tshwane, disappeared.The 29-year-old was last seen walking his girlfriend to a taxi stop on 10 December last year. His birthday was on 15 December.His girlfriend, Boitumelo Makhubela (29), told Lawrence’s parents that as her taxi drove off, she saw two unknown men approaching him. Little did she know then she was seeing him for the last time.if(typeof za24_DisplayAd != "undefined") za24_DisplayAd("300x250","2");var viewReq = new Array();function vu(u) {var i=new Image();i.src=u.replace("&amp;","&");viewReq.push(i);}vu("https://securepubads.g.doubleclick.net/pcs/view?xai\x3dAKAOjstmF2BqJ6FX6El84PCYDfJb9AajEm1CX1iQ-UiBp4cHYgjK9FreHNrWT3C92W0vsyQlO21Howt08zmHT_XfkWqsW8ubnm1aUm1f0cMMR3qMOxOIwPGM4pvafA3771keON8I61eAQC6Ol8oEt0tCZCJXPapWDAKpMib9rb3gurtoNIVRDbs700S5wLv21x_YSgFHKCA-fMrkr0mITN7SV8C2Dr7zX-IaU6g5pIj0CZfzPlAM7W2sR5vIsQ7SZ-64Us2VelaJHgLeuKVX6vhg6Bmu1dY40tY\x26sig\x3dCg0ArKJSzMrCHSOumOrsEAE\x26urlfix\x3d1\x26adurl\x3d")

   
